title: An Interview: Pure Sweat Basketball Podcast w/ Alan Stein
description: This one was a blast. Alan Stein is a vet in the performance coach space and just a stand-up dude. Loved this interview because we talked about life and business through the lens of sports which for those that know me, know I love so much !!
